{
  "source": "missed-class-policy.txt",
  "text": "Missed Class Make-Up Policy\r\n\r\nThe academy understands that students may occasionally miss scheduled classes.\r\n\r\nStudents may request make-up classes for missed sessions subject to the following conditions.\r\n\r\nEligibility\r\n\r\n- Make-up classes are only available for classes missed during the current calendar month.\r\n- Requests must be submitted before the end of the same month.\r\n- A student may attend a maximum of 2 make-up classes per month.\r\n\r\nAvailability\r\n\r\nMake-up classes are subject to coach availability, classroom capacity, and schedule compatibility.\r\n\r\nThe academy cannot guarantee a specific coach, batch, timing, or location for a make-up class.\r\n\r\nUnused Make-Ups\r\n\r\nUnused make-up opportunities cannot be carried forward to future months.\r\n\r\nMissed make-up classes are treated as consumed and cannot be rescheduled again.\r\n\r\nNon-Transferability\r\n\r\nMake-up classes are specific to the enrolled student and cannot be transferred to siblings, friends, or other students.\r\n\r\nExceptional Circumstances\r\n\r\nThe academy may approve additional make-up classes in exceptional circumstances at its sole discretion.",
